column3: This is a fix for http://youtrack.jetbrains.com/issue/IDEA-86919  and adds a filter for invalid elements to the built-in resource bundle editor.

I don't think it is necessary to do this anymore. This feature has been incorporated into IntelliJ around 2015, so this is obsolete now.  I have marked https://youtrack.jetbrains.com/issue/IDEA-86919 as obsolete now.
IDEA-86919 added filter which shows only invalid elements
